data.title: Ultrasonic Game Call
data.meta_description: Introducing FREQ™, the world’s first ultrasonic, full spectrum electronic game call. It operates like traditional e-callers but features two premium True Cast speakers, one low-frequency speaker that plays sounds at the end of the spectrum that humans can hear, and one ultrasonic speaker that plays high-frequency sounds. These speakers play full spectrum sound which was recorded on state-of-the-art recording equipment designed specifically to capture both low and high (ultrasonic) sounds. This patented technology is why FREQ dramatically outperforms ordinary e-callers and is exclusive to FREQ. There is nothing else like it available today!
data.text:
Unleash The World’s First True, Full Spectrum Ultrasonic Sounds

The Ultimate Ultrasonic Arsenal

FREQ™ Ultrasonic Game Calls come fully loaded with well over 200 distinct animal and bird sounds, most all of which are full spectrum, ultrasonic sounds. You'll get a variety of coyote and bobcat sounds, plus sounds that will attract a multitude of different game animals and birds. Plus, you'll get three pro call sequences compiled by game calling expert, Gary Roberson; one each for coyote, bobcat and fox that are each approximately 15 minutes long! Additionally, we will be continually producing more full spectrum, ultrasonic sounds that will be available for download to your FREQ call at no charge! So check back to the website to see what’s new!

Ultrasonic Game Calls:

The Most Effective and Realistic Electronic Call Ever Made

Ever since the advent of the electronic game call, we have been calling animals with sounds recorded and played back on equipment designed for what the human ear can hear. Now, for the first time ever, FREQ provides sounds recorded and played back on equipment capable of producing full spectrum, ultrasonic sound which is how animals hear!
